# ESP32 Firmware

## Hardware
- ESP32-WROOM
- DHT11 Sensor
- Soil Moisture Sensor
- Relay Module
- Water Pump

## Features
- Wi-Fi connectivity
- Firebase Realtime Database
- Automatic irrigation
- Temperature monitoring
- Humidity monitoring
- Soil moisture monitoring
- Device status reporting

## Pin Configuration

| Component | GPIO |
|----------|------|
| DHT11 | GPIO 4 |
| Soil Moisture | GPIO 34 |
| Relay | GPIO 26 |

## Upload

Open `DVR_Smart_Farming.ino` in Arduino IDE and upload to ESP32 after configuring your own Wi-Fi and Firebase credentials.
